Description_lang: Upon reaching 100 energy, Terros unleashes his volatile power with a brutal slam.This slam inflicts $381775s1 Nature damage to all players in a frontal cone, destroys $@spellname381486, and leaves $@spellname382458 in its wake.The cavern shutters from the force of the impact, inflicting an additional $386277s1 Nature damage to all players and causing $@spellname378861 to fall from the ceiling.
